sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>sn_customerservice.getAccountsProducts</api_name><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>getAccountsProducts</name><script><![CDATA[function getAccountsProducts(account) {
	var query = new GlideRecord('u_m2m_product_account');
	query.addQuery('u_account', account);
	query.query();
	
	var ans = [];
	
	while(query.next()) {
		ans.push(query.getValue('u_product'));
	}
	return 'sys_idIN' + ans.join();
	
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>tim_deniston</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-01-10 18:48:06</sys_created_on><sys_id>ad6d02abdbbae300bd00f8ecbf961983</sys_id><sys_mod_count>3</sys_mod_count><sys_name>getAccountsProducts</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Customer Service" source="sn_customerservice">51d811fad7223100b7490ee60e61034f</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Customer Service">51d811fad7223100b7490ee60e61034f</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_ad6d02abdbbae300bd00f8ecbf961983</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>tim_deniston</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-01-10 18:53:54</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
